---
---
<section id="systems">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">Architecture</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">How Our AI Agent System Works</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">A distributed network of specialized AI agents that work in concert to detect, investigate, and respond to threats faster than any human team could.</p>
    
    <div class="systems-flow">
      <div class="flow-card detect">
        <div class="flow-icon"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/></svg></div>
        <div class="flow-number">01</div>
        <h3>Detection Layer</h3>
        <p>AI agents continuously monitor SIEM, EDR, and network telemetry. Proprietary ML models score anomalies in real-time.</p>
        <ul class="flow-specs">
          <li>Sub-second threat detection</li>
          <li>99.7% detection accuracy</li>
          <li>Multi-source correlation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flow-connector">
        <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24"><path d="M0 12h30M25 6l10 6-10 6" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flow-card investigate">
        <div class="flow-icon"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a8 8 0 0 1 8 8c0 3.5-2 6-4 8h-8c-2-2-4-4.5-4-8a8 8 0 0 1 8-8z"/><path d="M9 22h6"/></svg></div>
        <div class="flow-number">02</div>
        <h3>Investigation Layer</h3>
        <p>When a threat is detected, autonomous agents conduct deep forensic analysis across threat intel, user behavior, and historical data.</p>
        <ul class="flow-specs">
          <li>Automated root cause analysis</li>
          <li>Contextual enrichment from 50+ sources</li>
          <li>Attack chain reconstruction</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flow-connector">
        <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24"><path d="M0 12h30M25 6l10 6-10 6" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flow-card respond">
        <div class="flow-icon"><svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg></div>
        <div class="flow-number">03</div>
        <h3>Response Layer</h3>
        <p>Actions are executed automatically: isolate endpoints, block IPs, revoke sessions, create tickets. All with full audit trails.</p>
        <ul class="flow-specs">
          <li>Average response time: 3 minutes</li>
          <li>Zero human intervention required</li>
          <li>Full SOC2 compliant logging</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="systems-integrations">
      <h3>Seamless Integration With Your Stack</h3>
      <div class="integrations-grid">
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">EDR</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">CrowdStrike, SentinelOne, Carbon Black</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">SIEM</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">Splunk, Microsoft Sentinel, Elastic</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">IAM</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">Okta, Azure AD, Ping Identity</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">Cloud</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">AWS, Azure, GCP Security Command Center</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">Ticketing</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">ServiceNow, Jira, PagerDuty</div>
        </div>
        <div class="integration-card">
          <div class="int-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3B7BF7" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="int-name">Network</div>
          <div class="int-vendors">Cisco, Palo Alto, Zscaler</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
#systems { background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, #0D1520 100%); }
.systems-flow {
  display: flex;
  align-items: stretch;
  gap: 0;
  margin: 3rem 0;
}
.flow-card {
  flex: 1;
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 2rem;
  position: relative;
  transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-spring), border-color 0.4s var(--ease-spring);
}
.flow-card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.02);
  border-color: rgba(59,123,247,0.6);
}
.flow-card.detect { border-top: 3px solid var(--blue); }
.flow-card.investigate { border-top: 3px solid #8B5CF6; }
.flow-card.respond { border-top: 3px solid var(--teal); }
.flow-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.flow-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
.flow-number {
  position: absolute;
  top: 1.5rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.flow-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.flow-card p { font-size: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.flow-specs { list-style: none; }
.flow-specs li {
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  padding: 0.375rem 0;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  position: relative;
}
.flow-specs li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--teal); }
.flow-connector {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 1rem;
}

.integrations-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}
.integration-card {
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.25rem;
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.4s var(--ease-spring);
}
.integration-card:hover { border-color: var(--blue); }
.int-icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; margin: 0 auto 0.75rem; }
.int-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
.int-name {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.int-vendors {
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .systems-flow { flex-direction: column; }
  .flow-connector { transform: rotate(90deg); padding: 1rem 0; }
  .integrations-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}
</style>